<h2 class="nounderline" id="maincontentlink">Get Involved</h2>

<p>
You can join PACER Center in being a champion for children with disabilities! Your donation of time, skills, or financial support will help PACER strengthen families and 
the community.
</p>

<h3><a href="volunteer/index.asp">Become a Volunteer</a></h3>
<p>Have a few spare hours? Help staff events, be a puppeteer, prepare mailings, or offer your other unique talents to PACER.</p>
<h3><a href="donate.asp">Make a Donation</a></h3>
<p>PACER welcomes donations in any form. Monetary gifts can be given online or by 
mail. You can also donate through planned gifts, memorials, vehicle donations, 
and more.</p>
<h3><a href="corporate.asp">Corporate Sponsors</a></h3>
<p>Your company can make an impact through financial contributions to the Hot 
Party, Annual Benefit, or specific PACER Programs; or through in-kind donations, 
knowledge, and expertise.</p>
<h3><a href="../benefit/index.asp">PACER's Annual Benefit</a></h3>
<p>PACER&rsquo;s Annual Benefit and Auction is a gala event which celebrates  families of children with disabilities while raising funds for PACER&rsquo;s  programs. The Benefit evening includes a fantastic performance by a major  entertainer, silent and live auctions, and a preconcert gourmet dinner  (ticketed separately), along with a few surprises! We hope you will join us! </p>
<h3><a href="events.asp">Special Events</a></h3>
<p>
PACER holds a variety of community events throughout the year, and community 
involvement is always appreciated through volunteers, corporate sponsorships, 
and attendance at the events!
</p>


